90%88%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%88%E8%88%87%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B%E5%8E%BB%E5%90%91-%E7%B7%B4%E4%B9%99%E9%8C%9A-&h=1674f4e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/時事要聞/article/20170728/2_533224_0/-氣短集-軸心突破-論聯合聲明失效與社運去向-練乙錚-</a>"}]}